    {
      "_id": "dcaf0a86b76008c1",
      "name": "Degrees of Damage",
      "sort": 2,
      "text": {
        "content": "<p id=\"2be1b90a-e081-8073-aa3a-e5a84e6355ad\">Each Attack has a base amount of damage that’s dealt on a Hit. This value is listed alongside the Weapon (see <strong>Equipment</strong>) or in the Spell’s description (see <strong>Spells</strong>). If the Check beats the targets Defense by 5 or more, the target takes extra damage and may suffer additional effects (see Check &amp; Save Outcomes for more information).</p>",
        "format": 1
