    {
      "_id": "4f4b79afd1784278",
      "name": "Damage Type Categories",
      "sort": 8,
      "text": {
        "content": "<p id=\"2be1b90a-e081-80d2-ba40-f1b507f56dfb\">Damage types (except True damage) are organized into the following categories: Physical, Elemental, and Mystical.</p><p id=\"2be1b90a-e081-80f1-9928-d82fbf70b35f\"><em><strong>Physical Damage:</strong></em> Includes Bludgeoning, Piercing, and Slashing damage.</p><p id=\"2be1b90a-e081-80dd-887b-e69bfaf340b1\" class=\"block-color-default_background\"><em><strong>Elemental Damage:</strong></em> Includes Cold, Corrosion, Fire, Lightning and Poison.</p><p id=\"2be1b90a-e081-804e-a243-fb926664ede4\"><em><strong>Mystical Damage:</strong></em> Includes Psychic, Radiant, and Umbral.</p>",
        "format": 1
      },
